title: Cartoon - Tex Avery - Jerky Turkey (1945)
description:
A WWII Home Front cartoon by Tex Avery. The Pilgrims land at Plymouth Rock and found a colony. A very large number of Pilgrims can be seen standing in line... for their cigarette rations. A Pilgrim goes hunting for Thanksgiving dinner. He meets a black market turkey.
